HP : 3K<br>
AC : Higher AC then well equiped lvl 50 warriors<br>
Melee DMG : 67 for quad attack, 25 for bash,kick<br>
Proc Spell DMG : 143 Cold base DD <br>
Casting Spell DMG : 84 Magic base 5.9 sec Stun DD<br>
DMG sheild : 50DS<br>
Faster then Jboots. If give sow, pet can run faster then any monsters <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Epic pet 's spells. - remember our pet lvl is 49,<br>
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>
<br>
ElementalMasteryBlast  Decrease Hit Points (HP) from 47 (L1) to 165 (L60) <br>
Classes: None <br>
Skill: Instantaneous <br>
Allowable Targets: All <br>
Range to Target: 150 feet <br>
Resistance Check: Cold <br>
Spell Duration: Instant <br>
Recast Delay: 6.0 seconds <br>
When someone casts: Soandso summons shards of elemental power. <br>
Spell cast on you: You are slashed by shards of elemental power. <br>
Spell cast on someone: Soandso is slashed by shards of elemental power. <br>
<br>
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>
<br>
ElementalMasteryStrike <br>
Stuns target between 3.1 (L1) to 5.9 (L42) seconds <br>
Decrease Hit Points (HP) from 36 (L1) to 95 (L60) <br>
Classes: None <br>
Skill: Instantaneous <br>
Allowable Targets: All <br>
Range to Target: 150 feet <br>
Resistance Check: Magic <br>
Spell Duration: Instant <br>
Recast Delay: 12.0 seconds <br>
When someone casts: Soandso summons a gust of pure elemental magic. <br>
Spell cast on you: You are stunned by a blast of pure elemental magic. <br>
Spell cast on someone: Soandso is stunned by a gust of pure elemental magic. <br>
Spell fades: You are no longer stunned. <br>
<br>
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>
<br>
AuraofElementalMastery   - <br>
Damage Shield from 2 (L1) to 61 (L60) <br>
Increase Fire Resist by 5 (L1) <br>
Classes: None <br>
Skill: Abjuration <br>
Allowable Targets: Self <br>
Resistance Check: Fire <br>
Spell Duration: Permanent <br>
Spell cast on you: You begin to radiate. <br>
Spell cast on someone: Soandso begins to radiate with an aura of Elemental Mastery. <br>
Spell fades: The radiation fades.<br>
